generate setup A first NTER last CT1

read coor card name "1acv_stripped_in_A.crd"

hbuild sele segid A .and. hydrogen end

ic para
ic build

hbuild sele segid A .and. hydrogen end

ic para
ic build

coor print sele segid A .and. .not. INIT end

read sequence coor name "1acv_stripped_in_B.crd" resid 
